<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email</title>

    <style>
        .bottom span {
            border-radius: 2px; 
            border: 1px solid grey; 
            padding: 5px 20px 5px 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .bottom span:hover {
            cursor: pointer;
            border: 1px solid peru; 
        }
        
        a:link { text-decoration: none; color: peru; }
        a:visited { text-decoration: none; }
        a:hover { text-decoration: none; color: peru;}
        a:active { text-decoration: none; }
    </style>

</head>

<body style="font-family: sans-serif; font-weight: 400;">
    <div class="container">

        <div style="width: 100%; height: 70px; background-color:lightgrey; display: flex; align-items: center; ">
            <span style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 20px; text-align:center;">
                <strong>Goread.io</strong>
            </span>
        </div>
        <div style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">
            <p><span>Hello there</span></p>
            <p><span>These items are still waiting for you.</span></p>
            <p><span>You can use Coupon code <strong>"FORGETME"</strong> to get an extra 10% discount.Please click on below given link to complete your purchase. -  <strong>Goread.io</strong></span></p>
            <p></p>
            <p><span>Here is your order information.</span></p>
        </div>
        
        <div style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; color: rgb(34,34,34)">
            <ul style="font-size: 14px; color: rgb(32,31,30); font-stretch: inherit; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit" width="650" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="5" border="1">
                <li>
                    <span style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" width="25%" bgcolor="#ffd966" align="right">
                        Email:
                    </span>
                    <span colspan="3" style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" align="left">
                        <%=data.email%>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" width="25%" bgcolor="#ffd966" align="right">
                        Instagram Account: 
                    </span>
                    <span colspan="3" style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" align="left">
                        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/<%=data.username%>"><%=data.username%></a>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" width="25%" bgcolor="#ffd966" align="right">
                        Amount: 
                    </span>
                    <span colspan="3" style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" align="left">
                        <strong><%=data.quantity%></strong>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" width="25%" bgcolor="#ffd966" align="right">
                        Package: 
                    </span>
                    <span colspan="3" style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" align="left">
                        <strong><%=data.name%></strong>
                    </span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" width="25%" bgcolor="#ffd966" align="right">
                        Manage your order link: 
                    </span>
                    <span colspan="3" style="font-family: Roboto,RobotoDraft,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; margin: 0px" align="left">
                        <a href="<%=data.link%>&email=<%=data.email%>&username=<%=data.username%>"><%=data.link%>&email=<%=data.email%>&username=<%=data.username%></a>
                    </span>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div style="font-family: Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 15px;">
            <p>It has been a pleasure doing business with you.</p>
            <p></p>
            <p>We wish you the best of luck.</p>
            <p></p>
            <p>Thanks and Best Regards!<br></p>
            <p></p>
        </div>
        <div class="bottom" style="width: 100%; padding-left: 40%;">
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>